Then you will definitely have a positive NPV

11:56.200 --> 12:00.200
So, if IRR

12:00.200 --> 12:02.200
Internal profitability rate

12:02.200 --> 12:03.200
This is the rule

12:03.200 --> 12:06.200
If IRR is more profitable

12:06.200 --> 12:07.200
More market profitability

12:07.200 --> 12:08.200
Or required profitability

12:08.200 --> 12:11.200
The project can be accepted

