We can also say that IRR is a kind of indicator of the project's strength, reliability, and stability

12:23.200 --> 12:26.200
It is a kind of a reserve of the project's strength

12:26.200 --> 12:30.200
The greater the difference between IRR and market profitability

12:30.200 --> 12:35.200
The more stable your project will be in the future

12:35.200 --> 12:37.200
The more reliable your project will be in the future

12:38.200 --> 12:41.200
We make investment decisions

12:41.200 --> 12:45.200
We are forced to predict the future, which is not determined

12:45.200 --> 12:53.200
Therefore, the more stable the project is in relation to the risk of changing the interest rate in the future

12:53.200 --> 12:55.200
The better

12:55.200 --> 12:59.200
Therefore, when making a decision, you must focus

12:59.200 --> 13:02.200
When making a decision, when choosing investment projects

13:02.200 --> 13:06.200
You must focus on the NPV, its absolute value

13:06.200 --> 13:08.200
The period of profitability

